2 entahamakargei miacum, == pind marmin
kamayakan pind marmin baghkacac e 2 maseric byureghacancy , electrons
Bnutyun => 4 poxazdecutyuner
grav, elmg, mijukayin ujegh tuyl
licqeri mijev ditarkel el.statik poxazdecutyun
arandzin qnnarkel ionneri xndiry, arandzin el. xndiry

1. Adiabat motavorutyun [bazmael molekulneri vra e ditarkvel heto teghapoxvel 
e pind marmni, vori himpum m(el zangvac)/M(mijuki ioni zangvac)<<1 if meki zangvacy aveli poqr e 
myusic => ka dandagh sharjvogh hamakarg ev shat arag sharjvogh elektronnei hamakarg. yur. ionneri dirqi popoxtutyun
el xndiry ditel ansharj ionneri dashtum, isk ionneri xndiry qnnarkel elektronneri mijinacvac dashtum. Adiabat
motavorutyuny hnaravorutyun e talis elektron ion iraric zad ditarkel u qnnarkel.
2. hrtri foki motavorutyamb artaqin pot dasht steghcelov steghcum enq nuyn dashty inch vor myus elektronneri azdecutyunnery (n-1) 
kulonyan poxazdecutyunnerov. Yur elektroni vra dashty azdum e summ ij e^2/|ri-rj| -> summ i u efective (ri)
erkusy miasin => gotineri tesutyun->bazmaelektronneri xndiry abstruction to mek elektronayin xndir.
Parberabar dashty steghcum en electron nery ionneri hamar.
